{
  "title": "Unrefined Greek Tofu Salad",
  "description": "An earthy, crumbly salad featuring char-grilled tofu, grapefruit vinaigrette, and a refreshing blend of Greek-inspired flavors.",
  "cuisine": "Greek",
  "diet": [
    "vegan",
